name: Objection formulée conformément à l'article 111, paragraphe 3: Critères d’examen technique supplémentaires - Objection pursuant to Rule 111(3): Additional technical screening criteria - Einwand gemäß Artikel 111 Absatz 3 GO: Festlegung zusätzlicher technischer Bewertungskriterien -  - Proposition de résolution
title: Additional technical screening criteria for determining the conditions under which certain economic activities qualify as contributing substantially to climate change mitigation or climate change adaptation and for determining whether those activities cause no significant harm to any of the other environmental objectives
